"{\"uid\": \"thesouthafrican.com-sport-paris-olympics-2024-south-africa-long-jumper-jovan-van-vuuren-receives-death-threats-on-eve-of-olympic-debut-breaking-news-result\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Copyright Blue Sky Publications (Pty) Ltd. All Rights Reserved.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 63, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 15, \"end\": 18, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"score\": 0.9962005102709282, \"rank\": 0.00232262165812706, \"text\": \"Sky\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"thesouthafrican.com is a division of Blue Sky Publications Ltd. Reproduction without permission prohibited  Home\\u00bbSport\\u00bbParis Olympics 2024\\u00bbSA long jumper Jovan van Vuuren receives death threats on eve of Olympic debut  South African long jumper Jovan van Vuuren has revealed that he was the victim of a personal attack which included death threats via WhatsApp.\", \"from\": 65, \"to\": 426, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 107, \"end\": 110, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"score\": 0.9962005102709282, \"rank\": 0.00232262165812706, \"text\": \"Sky\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\"}, {\"begin\": 417, \"end\": 425, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\", \"score\": 0.9999997229925086, \"rank\": 2.770073704378629e-07, \"text\": \"WhatsApp\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"South African long jumperJovan van Vuurenhas revealed that he was the victim of a personal attack which includeddeath threatsvia WhatsApp messages.\", \"from\": 428, \"to\": 575, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 557, \"end\": 565, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\", \"score\": 0.9999997229925086, \"rank\": 2.770073704378629e-07, \"text\": \"WhatsApp\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Enjoy the Paris Olympic Games 2024 experience at your favourite ATKV Resort!\", \"from\": 577, \"to\": 653, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 641, \"end\": 645, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ATKV\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"ATKV\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ATKV\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ATKV\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"According tooSuperSport, the messages were received on Saturday, the day before he was due to compete at his first Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 655, \"to\": 784, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"SASCOCreleased a statementin response to Van Vuuren's revelations, saying: \\\"Our Team SA long jumper Jovan van Vuuren competed in the men's qualification round at the 2024 Paris Olympics on Sunday against the backdrop of despicable threats dished out to himself and members of his family that were sent via WhatsApp.\", \"from\": 786, \"to\": 1101, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1092, \"end\": 1100, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\", \"score\": 0.9999997229925086, \"rank\": 2.770073704378629e-07, \"text\": \"WhatsApp\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The South African Sports Confederation and Olympic Committee (SASCOC) is aware of the threats and has offered unconditional support to the athlete.\", \"from\": 1103, \"to\": 1251, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He is also receiving professional counselling from Team SA's psychologists.\", \"from\": 1252, \"to\": 1327, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1308, \"end\": 1310, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.786441011319505e-20, \"text\": \"SA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In addition, the matter has been handed to the relevant authorities, including the police, for investigation.\\\"\", \"from\": 1328, \"to\": 1438, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For the latest Paris Olympics 2024 news, bookmarkThe South African website'sdedicated section for free-to-read content  Van Vuuren competed in the long jump qualifying and produced a best leap of 7.70m, which placed him 23rd overall, well off the top-12 spot he needed to get into the final  The 28-year-old said he did not want to make excuses for not making it through the long jump qualification on Sunday, but that he'd been mentally shaken by the messages, which reportedly included personal details about his family and his best friend who had died by suicide in 2018.\", \"from\": 1440, \"to\": 2014, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile,Cheswill Johnson, South Africa's other jumper, also failed to advance to the finals, struggling to find his rhythm and achieving a best of 4.49m.\", \"from\": 2016, \"to\": 2171, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2035, \"end\": 2042, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lyndon_B._Johnson\", \"score\": 0.9988656931312198, \"rank\": 0.0008301649992532818, \"text\": \"Johnson\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lyndon_B._Johnson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lyndon_B._Johnson\"}, {\"begin\": 2044, \"end\": 2056, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3153055708083492e-15, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This developing news 